# Project Scope

Before making changes, read `AGENTS.md` at the repository root.

Use it as the system-of-record for:
- project goals and constraints
- architecture boundaries
- documentation map
- reusable skills in `.agents/skills/`

For recurring workflows (adding a page, adding a project entry, updating profile copy), prefer the matching skill in `.agents/skills/` before inventing a new process.
